    <title><sourcexml>heading/title</sourcexml> to <targetxml>h</targetxml> <lnpid>id-CCCC-10250</lnpid></title>
    <body>
        <section>
            <p>When <sourcexml>heading/title</sourcexml> is the child of <sourcexml>bodytext</sourcexml>, then <sourcexml>heading/title</sourcexml> becomes <targetxml>h</targetxml>.</p>
        </section>
        <example>
            <title>Source XML</title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;bodytext&gt;
 &lt;heading searchtype="ANNOTATIONS"&gt;
  &lt;title&gt;&lt;emph typestyle="bf"&gt;NOTES&lt;/emph&gt;&lt;/title&gt;
 &lt;/heading&gt;
&lt;/bodytext&gt;

			</codeblock>
            <title>Target XML</title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;bodytext&gt;
 &lt;h&gt;&lt;emph typestyle="bf"&gt;NOTES&lt;/emph&gt;&lt;/h&gt;
&lt;/bodytext&gt;

            </codeblock>
        </example>
        <section><title>Changes</title></section>
    </body>
